  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for support of the International Boreal Conservation Campaign&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This special initiative renewal grant will support the Pew Trusts&#x2019; work with the International Boreal Conservation Campaign to secure permanent protection for half of Canada&#x2019;s 1.2 billion-acre boreal forest. The Hewlett Foundation has supported the trusts&#x2019; boreal protection since 2005. During that time, 388 million acres have been set aside under interim or permanent protection, and another 340 million have been pledged to be managed for sustainable use. In 2016, the campaign expects to secure protection for 10 million additional acres through provincial plans, and another 30 million acres to be designated for sustainable development.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
